comments: Nurkic (POR) firms up and absorbs the contact from Lowry (TOR) during the pick.
Nurkic (POR) puts his arm on the shoulder of Siakam (TOR), using him as leverage and affecting Siakam's ability to get the rebound.
Harkless (POR) makes marginal contact with Leonard (TOR) prior to him cleanly stealing the pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Gasol (TOR) enters the lane prior to the release of the free throw shot from Harkless (POR).
Layman (POR) makes marginal contact to the arm of Lowry (TOR), but the contact does not affect his control of the ball during the start of his drive.
[Observable in enhanced video] Lowry (TOR) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Gasol (TOR) makes marginal contact to the arm of Layman (POR) at the end of his drive that does not affect his ability to pass.
Nurkic (POR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Green (TOR) slightly extends his arms towards McCollum (POR) when they disengage but the contact does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Siakam (TOR) briefly grasps the arm of Nurkic (POR) during the pick, but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) moves laterally into Lillard's (POR) path and makes body to body contact that causes him to fall to the floor.
Lowry (TOR) briefly places his arms to the body of Harkless (POR) during the pick, but does not affect his ability to defend.
Harkless (POR) makes marginal contact to the arm of Lowry (TOR) at the start of his drive that does not affect his SQBR.

LAR shows Gasol (TOR) slightly extends his arms to the body of Nurkic (POR) as he steps in as the help defender during Lowry's (TOR) driving shot attempt, but the contact does not affect Nurkic's ability to defend the shot attempt.
Gasol (TOR) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Siakam (TOR) intentionally kicks the ball during Lillard's (POR) dribble.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Leonard (TOR) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Layman (POR) commits a take foul on Leonard (TOR).
Layman (POR) has his arms extended when he briefly engages with Leonard (TOR) but he immediately disengages.
Harkless (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of McCaw (TOR) and makes marginal contact to his body during the screen.
Lillard (POR) draws Lowry (TOR) into the air towards him and Lowry makes contact with Lillard's arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harkless (POR) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Lillard (POR) makes incidental contact to the body of Leonard (TOR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
